  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324820/extras/d338cc71a995f87946171561aafb6666.avif?t=1764490215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324820/extras_big/d338cc71a995f87946171561aafb6666.avif?t=1764490215 width=800 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Akuro and Bahaku were living happily in the jungle when, one day, darkness suddenly descended. So Akuro and Bahaku set out on a journey to find a way to combat the darkness...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore unknown realms in hand-drawn shaman tents, elf forests, magical caves, and celestial starfields.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve various puzzles to obtain items to combat the darkness.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Akuro and Bahaku defeat the darkness and return to a peaceful life.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324820/extras/d338cc71a995f87946171561aafb6666.avif?t=1764490215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324820/extras_big/d338cc71a995f87946171561aafb6666.avif?t=1764490215 width=800 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Akuro and Bahaku were living happily in the jungle when, one day, darkness suddenly descended. So Akuro and Bahaku set out on a journey to find a way to combat the darkness...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore unknown realms in hand-drawn shaman tents, elf forests, magical caves, and celestial starfields.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve various puzzles to obtain items to combat the darkness.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Akuro and Bahaku defeat the darkness and return to a peaceful life.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
